name: Farm Invasion
description:
You're a farmer with a small field and a cow. There's aliens and a UFO. Buy guns from the trailer trash gun shop and kill the alien scum! The aliens want to kill your cow, defend her at all cost. Avoid the UFO and try to survive the farm invasion! 

Made possible by this Udemy course: https://www.udemy.com/course/how-to-make-a-retro-style-3d-fps-in-the-godot-game-...
